The NHL Commissioner has released a statement expressing condolences and mourning the loss of Gaudreau, a highly skilled player known for his exceptional speed and playmaking abilities. The hockey world is in shock and disbelief, as fans and fellow athletes pay tribute to the talented Gaudreau and his brother.

summary: Manchester United has secured the signing of Uruguayan midfielder Manuel Ugarte from Paris Saint-Germain. The transfer marks United's sixth signing of the summer, with Ugarte joining a squad aiming to challenge for trophies. Despite speculation about his potential debut against Liverpool, Ugarte is expected to sit out that match due to visa issues. The 21-year-old has signed a five-year contract with United, with a fee rising up to £51 million. Ugarte's addition is expected to bolster United's midfield, but questions remain whether he can address the team's ongoing issues in that area.
